AP Alternative Assets, L.P.
AP Alternative Assets, L.P. is a closed-end limited partnership established under the laws of Guernsey. It is subject to the ongoing supervision of the Guernsey Financial Services Commission (“GFSC”). The website of the GFSC can be accessed at www.gfsc.gg.


AP Alternative Assets, L.P. is a limited partnership established under the laws of Guernsey (registered number 621). Its registered office is at Trafalgar Court, Les Banques, St. Peter Port, Guernsey, GY1 3QL. Save as mentioned below, references to “AP Alternative Assets, L.P.”, “we” and “our” are to AP Alternative Assets, L.P.

Disclaimers and Exclusion of Liability
Our manager, Apollo Alternative Assets, L.P., acts for the funds and clients it manages or advises and not for anyone else. It will not act for, advise or be responsible for providing protections afforded to its customers to anyone other than such funds and clients.


